Dev/Test Environment Scheduling

Dev environments
don't need to run 24/7:

Schedule:
  Start  : Mon-Fri 8am
  Stop   : Mon-Fri 8pm
  Weekend: OFF

Savings:
  Running 60hrs/week
  instead of 168hrs/week
  saves 64% on dev costs ✅

AWS Instance Scheduler
or Lambda + CloudWatch Events ✅
